&quot;Parkroad Family, Child and Sexual Offences Unit are looking for Andries Albertus De Villiers(47) known as 'Albert' who can assist the police in two separate rape cases that happened in Bloemfontein 2006 and Kwazulu-Natal 2015,&quot; said Constable Maselela Langa in a statement. &quot;Albert was last seen in Brits and now it believed that he is in Durban.&quot;&nbsp;Police said anyone who might know his whereabouts can contact Investigating Officer Detective WO Arlene Snyman on 082 527 7063 or 082 301 6390. African News Agency